title: MUMBLE_CLEAR_VOICE_TARGET_CHANNELS
content:
0x5EA72E76// MumbleClearVoiceTargetChannels
void MUMBLE_CLEAR_VOICE_TARGET_CHANNELS(int targetId);Parameters:targetId: A Mumble voice target ID, ranging from 1..30 (inclusive).Clears channels from the target list for the specified Mumble voice target ID.
